01:53.405 --> 01:54.947
The nails have to be clipped,

01:55.032 --> 01:57.283
shaped and brought
back to life.

01:57.367 --> 02:01.204
And you must cast
the nails to the person.

02:01.288 --> 02:02.830
You wouldn't
want a mechanic

02:02.915 --> 02:03.998
to have the nails
of a flight attendant.

02:04.082 --> 02:05.124
Would you?

02:06.627 --> 02:07.627
[Blows quickly]

02:07.711 --> 02:09.753
[Machine buzzing]

02:09.838 --> 02:11.839
It is very important
to remove any
unwanted nasal,

02:11.924 --> 02:16.385
ear, or facial hair.

02:16.470 --> 02:18.387
We can never be too vigilant

02:18.472 --> 02:24.018
