they want one last look
at this miraculous world.

02:34.238 --> 02:36.405
But with some Super Glue...

02:36.490 --> 02:39.075
a little dab will do you...

02:39.159 --> 02:42.578
and it's no more peeking.

02:42.663 --> 02:46.958
Even though the features
have been set during
the embalming,

02:47.042 --> 02:48.960
you have
to reassess
and readjust

02:49.044 --> 02:56.217
because of continuing
emaciation and dehydration.

02:56.301 --> 02:58.302
Perfect expression
of the mouth

02:58.387 --> 03:01.848
would be relaxed, natural,
with a little bit
of a smile.

03:01.932 --> 03:04.767
