unhappy to be there.

03:04.852 --> 03:08.729
And we must always be on guard
for the mischievous lip drift.

03:08.814 --> 03:11.941
Even the slightest
hint of teeth can
be disastrous.

03:12.025 --> 03:17.613
You cannot have grief
tragically become
a comedy.

03:17.698 --> 03:20.324
