01:08:58.968 --> 01:09:01.053
No way.

01:09:01.136 --> 01:09:04.723
Well, it was
fucking unbelievable.
Nobody could believe it.

01:09:04.808 --> 01:09:07.725
You know, I could see
somebody wantin'
to do that to her,

01:09:07.810 --> 01:09:10.687
