01:10:05.076 --> 01:10:08.078
No body,
no arrest.

01:10:08.162 --> 01:10:10.289
A woman like that
with a bad heart...

01:10:10.373 --> 01:10:13.125
he shoulda just shoved
the pillow right
over her face.

01:10:13.209 --> 01:10:15.627
Then they probably wouldn't
even done an autopsy.

01:10:15.712 --> 01:10:17.921
A few days later,
he'd be doing
her funeral.

01:10:18.006 --> 01:10:20.048
Oh, I just started
shaking my head

01:10:20.133 --> 01:10:22.551
going, "Oh Bernie,
Bernie, Bernie, Bernie."

01:10:22.635 --> 01:10:25.721
Who in their right mind
would kill their meal ticket?

01:10:25.805 --> 01:10:27.639
It was crazy
around here.

01:10:27.724 --> 01:10:31.476
People were on Danny Buck
like ticks on a coon dog.

01:10:31.561 --> 01:10:33.478
