01:11:16.773 --> 01:11:18.440
she had it
coming to her.

01:11:18.524 --> 01:11:20.734
It's not as bad as
people say it is.

01:11:20.818 --> 01:11:23.862
He only shot her
four times,
not five.

01:11:23.947 --> 01:11:25.364
You know what?

01:11:25.448 --> 01:11:27.324
You people are
as crazy as a coot.

01:11:27.408 --> 01:11:29.910
I like Bernie Tiede
as much as you do.

01:11:29.994 --> 01:11:33.330
He did shoot
her though!

01:11:33.414 --> 01:11:35.374
I tell you what.

01:11:35.458 --> 01:11:36.959
I don't claim
to know what
Bernie did

01:11:37.043 --> 01:11:38.794
or did not do.

01:11:38.878 --> 01:11:41.171
I figure that's
between him and
God Almighty.

01:11:41.255 --> 01:11:43.882
Mm-hm. And the
way I figure it,

01:11:43.967 --> 01:11:46.760
that's where it
should stay.

01:11:46.844 --> 01:11:50.889
Man, I hope
I'm on that jury.

01:11:50.974 --> 01:11:54.893
Yes, we need to be able
to forgive someone who's
done something wrong.

01:11:54.978 --> 01:11:57.312
And no matter what
the truth is,

01:11:57.397 --> 01:12:01.566
Bernie is going
to need our prayers.

01:12:01.651 --> 01:12:04.027
So, folks, we
need to understand

01:12:04.112 --> 01:12:08.365
that tragedies
are simply tests
of our faith.

01:12:08.449 --> 01:12:10.534
And right now,
Bernie needs to know,

01:12:10.618 --> 01:12:15.163
especially during this
testing of his faith,

01:12:15.248 --> 01:12:19.126
that God
and this congregation

01:12:19.210 --> 01:12:22.879
have not
abandoned him.

01:12:22.964 --> 01:12:24.715
[Buck clears throat]

01:12:24.799 --> 01:12:26.008
