four times

01:12:56.956 --> 01:12:58.457
and put in the freezer.

01:12:58.541 --> 01:13:00.208
Danny, the Bernie
you're talking about

01:13:00.293 --> 01:13:02.544
is not the Bernie
this church knows.

01:13:02.628 --> 01:13:04.671
The heck it isn't.

01:13:04.756 --> 01:13:06.840
It sounds like
the only Bernie you're
choosing to remember

01:13:06.924 --> 01:13:09.926
is the one that
donated 100,000 dollars
to your church. Reverend.

01:13:10.011 --> 01:13:12.304
Danny, look,
I'm sorry you
feel that...

01:13:12.388 --> 01:13:15.474
It's been hard
on everyone.

01:13:15.558 --> 01:13:17.476
Alright, kiddos.

01:13:17.560 --> 01:13:19.144
All the good
that Bernie had done
for everybody,

01:13:19.228 --> 01:13:21.855
or for us around here,
it just...

01:13:21.939 --> 01:13:23.982
they come in,
and then it was
gonna get all

01:13:24.067 --> 01:13:27.110
Mrs. Nugent's money
back that Bernie
had spent.

01:13:27.195 --> 01:13:29.112
We lost our airport,

01:13:29.197 --> 01:13:32.324
we lost our best store,

01:13:32.408 --> 01:13:36.369
cars, some people
lost their houses,

01:13:36.454 --> 01:13:39.331
jet skis.

01:13:39.415 --> 01:13:42.501
He spent 600,000 dollars
of Mrs. Nugent's money.

01:13:52.428 --> 01:13:53.845
No paperwork, anything?

01:13:53.930 --> 01:13:56.014
A receipt [inaudible]?

01:13:56.099 --> 01:13:57.891
I don't know,
I mean...

01:13:57.975 --> 01:14:00.477
he just gave it to me,
said I could have it.

01:14:04.524 --> 01:14:06.233
Well, you know, at least
they could've left

01:14:06.317 --> 01:14:07.526
some money for the church.

01:14:07.610 --> 01:14:11.029
Hell, [unintelligible].

01:14:11.114 --> 01:14:12.614
(female voice)
Here they come!

01:14:12.698 --> 01:14:14.991
[Cheering]

01:14:15.076 --> 01:14:17.661
(female reporter, off)
Although rumors have
been circulating

01:14:17.745 --> 01:14:19.454
about a possible
plea bargain

01:14:19.539 --> 01:14:21.790
to lesser charges
or a probated sentence,

01:14:21.874 --> 01:14:23.959
District Attorney
Danny Buck Davidson

01:14:24.043 --> 01:14:26.169
has shocked East Texas

01:14:26.254 --> 01:14:28.547
by filing first degree
murder charges
against Tiede,

01:14:28.631 --> 01:14:31.049
which could result
in a life sentence.

01:14:31.134 --> 01:14:33.093
[Shouting]

01:14:33.177 --> 01:14:35.137
Clearly, the tiny
town of Carthage
is buzzing

01:14:35.221 --> 01:14:37.139
with opinions
over the murder.

01:14:37.223 --> 01:14:40.100
He didn't shoot
Mrs. Nugent in
the back.

01:14:40.184 --> 01:14:41.560
