convict him
of anything

01:14:53.322 --> 01:14:55.490
and I'll say
this, if a jury
as to convict him,

01:14:55.575 --> 01:14:57.325
they'll probably gonna
give him probation.

01:14:57.410 --> 01:14:59.202
